('', 'Preface', 'Advances in Intelligent Systems and Computing ', '2018', '583', 'v-vi', '451317328NA', '', 'Department of Applied Science and Engineering, IIT Roorkee, Saharanpur, India; Department of Physics Amity School of Applied Sciences, Amity University Rajasthan, Jaipur, Rajasthan, India; Department of Computer Science and Engineering, Amity School of Engineering and Technology, Amity University Rajasthan, Jaipur, Rajasthan, India; Department of Electronics and Communication Engineering SEEC, Manipal University Jaipur, Jaipur, Rajasthan, India; Surface Characterization Group, NIMS Nano Characterization Unit, Advanced Key Technologies Division, Tsukuba, Ibaraki, Japan', '', '', '', 'Springer Verlag', '21945357', '9789811056864', '', '', 'Editorial', '', 'SCOPUS', '', '', '', ''),
